      "span_text": "Consistent with our previously established rat model  of fetal growth restriction with maternal UN, we demonstrated a main effect of maternal diet on maternal weight gain during pregnancy and lactation (P < 0.0001), where UN dams were significantly lighter than CON dams during pregnancy and lactation from day 5-35 post coitus (P < 0.001) based on Bonferroni post hoc analysis (Supplemental Figure 1A ).",
